WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:31.300 --> 00:00:35.410
Hi guys, I'm Amaury Lavernhe, 28 years old
from Reunion Island.

00:00:35.410 --> 00:00:39.400
Sponsored by Sniper Bodyboard, Agent Eighteen
and Micro Nutrition.

00:00:58.210 --> 00:01:02.390
So my main inspiration to design my dream
wave is the wave I'm surfing the most the

00:01:02.390 --> 00:01:08.250
last 2 years: Fronton in the Canary Islands.This
wave is amazing for bodyboarding, I love to

00:01:08.250 --> 00:01:12.200
push my limits there and it's always a challenge,
especially when it's big.

00:01:22.710 --> 00:01:27.789
So my dream wave would be a mix between Fronton
and a white sandy beach. So imagine a heavy

00:01:27.789 --> 00:01:34.789
take off at Fronton, heavy pits, big ramps
and then keep going to another section on the sand bar.

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:04.000
This is my dream wave, hope you guys like it.

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:06.030
This is online at www.youriding.com.

